尼欧还曾为[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]、[[席琳·迪翁|席琳·迪翁]]、[[安娜塔西亚|安娜塔西亚]]、[[席亚拉|席亚拉]]、[[柯賓·布魯|柯賓·布魯]]和[[安立奎·伊格萊西亞斯|安立奎·伊格萊西亞斯]]写过歌。<ref name="HobbsSex"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-30904347_ITM|title=The many roles of Ne-Yo|last=McDonald|first=Sam|date=2007-05-30|work=Daily Press|publisher=AccessMyLibrary|accessdate=2008-12-24|archive-date=2009-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112080247/http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-30904347_ITM|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还和[[琳賽·蘿涵|琳賽·蘿涵]]合作，已经完成了“Bossy”一曲，作为新专辑《Spirit in the Dark》中的单曲先行发售。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20198406,00.html|title=Listen to Lindsay Lohan's New Song 'Bossy'|last=Laudadio|first=Marisa|coauthors=Herndon, Jessica|date=2008-05-07|work=People|accessdate=2008-12-24|archive-date=2008-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216123825/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20198406,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>尼欧还证实，制作人[[will.i.am|will.i.am]]曾和他接洽，为[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]的新专辑写歌。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2007/06/07/ne_yo_i_m_not_trying_to_top_thriller |title=Ne-Yo: 'I'm Not Trying To Top 'Thriller' |date=2007-06-07 |publisher=Starpulse |accessdate=2008-12-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216124117/http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2007/06/07/ne_yo_i_m_not_trying_to_top_thriller |archivedate=2008-12-16 }}</ref>可是在杰克逊死的时候，尼欧同他的合作仍然只是停留在创作阶段。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.soulofrnb.com/?p=893|title=Michael Jackson Tribute Tour by The Jacksons, Final Collaborations With NeYo'|date=2009-07-03|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-date=2011-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718001959/http://www.soulofrnb.com/?p=893|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2009年，他为日本流行组合[[w-inds.|w-inds.]]写了“Truth (Saigo no Shinjitsu)”一曲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/confidence/70187/full/|title=Oricon Style – United States 节奏布鲁斯 Artist Ne-Yo adds another name to w-inds. roster(Japanese)|date=2009-10-30|accessdate=2009-10-31|archive-date=2009-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091102131713/http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/confidence/70187/full|dead-url=no}}</ref>

